name: Treehouse AVAX
description: tAVAX is a liquid staking token (LST) is an independent extension of the successful tETH concept into the Avalanche (AVAX) ecosystem. It is designed to bring similar yield optimization and liquidity benefits to AVAX stakers, enabling users to earn rewards while maintaining flexibility across DeFi applications. tAVAX will also be part of Treehouse's Decentralized Offered Rates (DOR) ecosystem in the future.
